{"tid":2203540,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無ching明白拉鏈出軌個種痛苦","createTime":"2020-09-15T11:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T14:05:34.000Z","uid":218575,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a54c32044c8cf310649bc4882fd2305b563f353a","tid":2203540,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:43:36.000Z","msg":"今日番緊放lunch起身走個時<br />\n一起身個時聽到「渣」一聲<br />\n以為係爆肽 點知check check下先知<br />\n係爆咗拉鏈 係爆到挽救唔到個隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmGeeAE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmGeeAE.png&h=89738ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連lunch都無去食到<br />\n係到研究咗成粒鐘<br />\n啲同事食完飯番黎 俾佢地發現咗<br />\n又鬼死咁好心熱情幫我研究<br />\n引咗成班十幾個同事 <br />\n係到圍觀我下體 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個又話用釘書機 一個又話用膠紙痴住先<br />\n最後用咗個最可行嘅方法 三個扣針扣住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知最後收工搭巴士返屋企 <br />\n一坐底都係爆開 有三個窿<br />\n見到對面兩個呀姐係到陰陰嘴笑<br />\n個下心情真係跌到落谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5a6405bb460ff74544606897ec03932b17bc1b","tid":2203540,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"樓主幾重"},{"pid":"f3204466fff579796d603789ed08cdbfb4760661","tid":2203540,"uid":5883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"感情台？ 娛樂台下話？"},{"pid":"7ca3a16495ae59a52a67b6a9b03ed7ea438eceff","tid":2203540,"uid":376052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971f51df4ebaf2255a494aaaab8d404a4bfe4783","tid":2203540,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:18:05.000Z","msg":"要除咗條褲先至處理得好"},{"pid":"956e4cc35961e03ef791f739c4532721b61fe016","tid":2203540,"uid":363208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"減肥啦"},{"pid":"575eb347dbc2e73337b3817638f359cecc62dcf0","tid":2203540,"uid":245782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"試過條西褲褲袋爆開左<br />\n喺公司求其搵膠紙痴住<br />\n落街食飯、去廁所都鬼鬼鼠鼠<br />\n但係行得太快既話痴住個個位又爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}